1
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:34,970
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:39,390
[2010]

3
00:01:37,950 --> 00:01:40,070
This company can take care of
household registration.

4
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:41,530
And this foreign company—

5
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,780
it should pay pretty well, right?

6
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,000
You'd better consider

7
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,060
your grades first.

8
00:01:46,229 --> 00:01:48,479
Everyone wants to get into
those good companies.

9
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:49,640
It's not that easy.

10
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:52,039
Wang from the School of Management

11
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:53,920
requested a song

12
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:55,400
for the graduating seniors—

13
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,870
"My Future Is Not a Dream."

14
00:01:57,039 --> 00:02:01,150
♪ Are you like me,
lowering your head under the sun? ♪

15
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:01,280
This song is so old.

16
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,040
I don't want to work hard

17
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:07,820
♪ Working hard quietly
in streaming sweat ♪

18
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,240
with tears in my eyes.

19
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:15,280
♪ Are you like me,
even being treated indifferently ♪

20
00:02:17,890 --> 00:02:23,230
♪ Still won't give up the life
you desire ♪

21
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:23,250
[Episode 10]
[My Future Is Not a Dream]

22
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,340
You are from Yunan?

23
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,490
I know that place very well.

24
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,000
I used to work there.

25
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:33,760
What a coincidence.

26
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,380
So why did you come to Shengcheng?

27
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,680
My daughter graduated from university.

28
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,030
She wants to start her career
in Shengcheng,

29
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,430
so we came to check it out.

30
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,960
I run a small clothing business.

31
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:48,079
I was thinking of going to Longcheng
to restock,

32
00:02:48,079 --> 00:02:49,210
so we came together.

33
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:51,400
You say
your daughter is a university graduate?

34
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,260
That's really quite impressive.

35
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,750
It seems you really have a way

36
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:56,950
of raising children.

37
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,500
It's mainly to her own credit.

38
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:02,870
Our Xiaolan

39
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:03,870
has had it tough.

40
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,910
We are just farmers working the land.

41
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:08,370
We couldn't help her much.

42
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,080
She relied entirely on herself.

43
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,080
What's wrong with being a farmer?

44
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,520
I come from a farming background too.

45
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,240
Back then,

46
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,240
I worked in Yunan.

47
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,910
There's a lot of delicious food in Yunan,

48
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:16,910
like mutton soup,

49
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:17,740
spicy soup,

50
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,910
and pan-fried buns.

51
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:19,310
Yeah.

52
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:22,410
Did you call your uncle?

53
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:23,710
Once Mayor Tang wakes up,

54
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:25,110
we can go back to the city.

55
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:26,680
Mayor Tang?

56
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,960
Mr. Tang in there

57
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,960
is the new Vice Mayor of Shengcheng.

58
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,630
Just now, when his driver

59
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,360
was on the phone,

60
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,220
I overheard it.

61
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,150
I'll go pay the fees.

62
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:38,480
Okay.

63
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:39,120
Okay.

64
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:44,120
Mr. Tang,

65
00:03:44,150 --> 00:03:45,880
we brought you some breakfast.

66
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:46,750
Thank you.

67
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,280
Mrs. Liu.

68
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:49,120
Alright.

69
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,120
Miss Xia Xiaolan.

70
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:52,070
Thank you.

71
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:54,150
We really are fated to meet.

72
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:56,310
Who would've thought we'd run into
each other again

73
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:57,870
under these circumstances?

74
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:58,840
You remember me?

75
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:01,560
Please, have a seat.

76
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:01,960
Okay.

77
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,360
That brave and resourceful

78
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,360
young lady

79
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:09,910
who dared to take on that bad guy

80
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,770
all by herself—

81
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,200
how could I not remember?

82
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,000
I heard from your mother

83
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:17,070
that you graduated from
Huaqing's Architecture Department.

84
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:18,360
So why did you come here?

85
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,630
Construction is ongoing everywhere
in Shengcheng.

86
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:23,070
I'm sure I'll find a place
where my skills can be put to use.

87
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,470
You want to build houses?

88
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,690
You've got no money

89
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:28,960
and no connections.

90
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:32,000
You think you can build houses
just because you want to?

91
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,800
Well, right now,

92
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,120
I definitely can't build houses.

93
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,800
But with so many already built,

94
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,190
they'll need interior finishing, right?

95
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:38,730
I'll start little by little—

96
00:04:38,730 --> 00:04:39,680
one day, I'll have the connections

97
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,680
and the capital.

98
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,190
Do you think Ke Yixiong

99
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,870
is out of his mind?

100
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,680
He asked me to set up a meeting with you

101
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:53,010
and said he wants to do business together.

102
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,480
He sees you're doing well

103
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,010
and wants a piece of the pie.

104
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:57,680
But it seems

105
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,920
he has no sense of

106
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,120
his own character.

107
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:02,070
I'm partnering with you, Sis Bai,

108
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,560
because you have a good character.

109
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,430
But what would I want from Ke Yixiong?

110
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:07,390
Should I admire the fact that
he once snatched Kang Wei's bag,

111
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:09,990
or that he tried to abduct me
in broad daylight?

112
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,190
The Longcheng Train Station

113
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,360
is getting more and more chaotic.

114
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,100
It's crawling with Ke Yixiong's men.

115
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:19,070
Who knows

116
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,480
what other shady business they're up to

117
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,630
besides stealing?

118
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:22,720
We'd better

119
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:24,560
stay away from people like him.

120
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,250
But I don't think he's going to give up.

121
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,800
If I really make it big in Shengcheng

122
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,800
in the future,

123
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,680
there'll only be more and more people
getting jealous.

124
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,740
This one. This one.

125
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:39,510
You look so gorgeous.

126
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:42,240
This piece's really nice.
When did you buy it?

127
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:42,870
I see people wearing pretty dresses

128
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:44,310
all over Shengcheng.

129
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,610
I can't fall behind.

130
00:05:46,150 --> 00:05:47,159
So you really plan

131
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:49,520
to come to Shengcheng after you graduate?

132
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,240
Actually, the first time
I went to Longcheng

133
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,950
to stock up on goods,

134
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:53,350
I already made up my mind—

135
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,120
I was definitely

136
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,850
coming here after graduation.

137
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:57,510
Longcheng is already

138
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,920
quite developed now,

139
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,160
while Shengcheng still has

140
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,190
a lot of room for growth.

141
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:03,590
So, are you closing your shop
in Jingcheng?

142
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,000
As for my shop in Jingcheng,

143
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,310
I'm leaving it to my aunt.

144
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:09,680
My mom and I will open a new shop here.

145
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:10,870
When I go back to Longcheng tomorrow,

146
00:06:10,870 --> 00:06:11,560
I want to visit

147
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,160
the wholesale market again.

148
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:17,120
But you majored in architecture.
Are you giving up on building houses?

149
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,680
Building houses

150
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,630
requires money and land.

151
00:06:20,660 --> 00:06:21,950
I have neither right now,

152
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:23,720
so I'll start with what I'm familiar with.

153
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,480
I'll save money

154
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,600
while looking for opportunities.

155
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,040
Got it?

156
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:28,070
Alright, enough talk about work.

157
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:30,400
I'm going to take a shower
and get changed.

158
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:51,570
You look so pretty.

159
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:52,580
Thanks.

160
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,390
So are you, Sis Bai.

161
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,270
So cool.

162
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,750
Bootlicker.

163
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:58,820
I mean you're sucking up to me.

164
00:06:59,530 --> 00:07:00,040
Sis Bai.

165
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:01,720
Where are we going tonight?

166
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,680
I'll show you guys Shengcheng's

167
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,270
most happening spot.

168
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:07,390
Let's go.

169
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:07,920
Let's go.

170
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,920
Come on.

171
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,600
What do you think—exciting or not?

172
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:26,480
♪ It'll be dark in a minute  ♪

173
00:07:27,010 --> 00:07:29,400
♪ Don't rush to success ♪

174
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:33,230
♪ Time flies so fast like lightning ♪

175
00:07:34,210 --> 00:07:36,330
♪ If you want to be happy,
get out on the streets ♪

176
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:40,260
♪ No need to turn down the volume ♪

177
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:43,470
♪ The lamps sway gently in the wind
at dusk ♪

178
00:07:44,190 --> 00:07:47,340
♪ My little beige headphones
blink in comfort ♪

179
00:07:48,270 --> 00:07:50,880
♪ My legs just won't stay still ♪

180
00:07:52,670 --> 00:07:54,670
♪ Tomorrow seems so far away ♪

181
00:07:54,690 --> 00:07:56,420
♪ The world keeps spinning ♪

182
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,510
Order whatever you want to eat

183
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:59,420
♪ Do you wanna dance tonight? ♪

184
00:07:58,510 --> 00:07:59,870
or drink today.

185
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,720
It's all on me.

186
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:01,660
♪ Tomorrow seems so far away ♪

187
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,030
You're too generous today, Sis Bai.

188
00:08:02,170 --> 00:08:03,420
♪ Everything is spinning ♪

189
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,190
This is where young people hang out.

190
00:08:03,810 --> 00:08:06,530
♪ Do you want to hold me tight? ♪

191
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,070
It's not expensive.

192
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:07,000
From what I know about you,

193
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:10,910
♪ Ho Yuet-tai, Chan Po-lai, Ng Yuen-tsai ♪

194
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,950
this must be your first time here too,
right?

195
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:10,120
Well, what's fun in

196
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,830
singing and dancing

197
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:11,510
alone?

198
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:13,000
It's way better coming with a group.

199
00:08:12,110 --> 00:08:13,690
♪ Ngai Shuk-fai, Szehung Man-wai ♪

200
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:17,950
♪ Snakes and ants, Lau Ping-tai,
and the Gods combined ♪

201
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,800
Since we're here,

202
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,520
sing us a song. Sing us a song.

203
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:17,830
I'm not a good singer.

204
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:19,070
Sing one. Go on.

205
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:20,390
Don't be nervous, Sis Bai.

206
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:23,940
♪ All of them start dancing, feet up,
legs turning and heads twisting ♪

207
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:21,120
My mom says,

208
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:21,600
when you're nervous,

209
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,120
just pretend the audience are potatoes.

210
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,830
Then you won't be nervous.

211
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:24,680
I... I'll go pick a song.

212
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:29,700
♪ Do you wanna dance tonight? ♪

213
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,600
Let's sing together.

214
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,190
Go on. Go on.

215
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:27,720
-Alright, alright.
-Okay.

216
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:39,120
♪ Are you like me,
lowering your head under the sun? ♪

217
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:46,650
♪ Working hard quietly
in streaming sweat ♪

218
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:53,910
♪ Are you like me,
even being treated indifferently ♪

219
00:08:56,250 --> 00:09:01,930
♪ Still won't give up the life
you desire ♪

220
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:08,190
♪ I know my future is not a dream ♪

221
00:09:09,250 --> 00:09:12,150
♪ I live every minute to its fullest ♪

222
00:09:13,170 --> 00:09:15,650
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

223
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:19,890
♪ My heart dances with hope ♪

224
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:24,330
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

225
00:09:24,350 --> 00:09:27,640
♪ I live every minute to its fullest ♪

226
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,610
Look, Xiaolan.

227
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,120
These are all private

228
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,870
residences.

229
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:32,320
Nowadays in Shengcheng,

230
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,030
there are many developers

231
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,480
building this kind of commercial housing,

232
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,080
so the demand for
private interior renovation

233
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,550
is huge.

234
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:38,270
Okay.

235
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,630
Did you archive these cases?

236
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,120
Yes.

237
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:41,630
Look, I have the camera with me.

238
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:42,910
All the photos before renovation,

239
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:43,960
during the process, and after inspection

240
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,820
are all in here.

241
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:46,830
[Renmin Bridge Small Commodities Market]

242
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,440
Put the everyday items together,

243
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,600
and group together the ones

244
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,120
with the same price.

245
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,080
It makes it easier for you to track,

246
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,240
and easier for customers to choose.

247
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:56,670
Got it.

248
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,960
Actually, the appliances
and general goods here

249
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,720
are similar to those in Jingcheng,

250
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,150
but the clothes here

251
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:05,030
are indeed more stylish.

252
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,080
This city is close to Gangdao,

253
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,750
so there are many merchants
from Gangdao and abroad here.

254
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,440
What they wear and use

255
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,770
influences the locals.

256
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,790
So people here

257
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,270
care more about fashion,

258
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:14,670
and are more willing to spend on it.

259
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,230
So is it even tougher

260
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:17,600
for us to open a shop here?

261
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,870
As long as we find

262
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:20,440
our own niche and specialty,

263
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,370
it won't be hard.

264
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:29,800
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

265
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,200
But your line of thinking

266
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,240
may not be best for the client.

267
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,510
That's the only way to maximize our odds.

268
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:03,870
Otherwise, if any step in the process

269
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:04,550
goes wrong...

270
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:05,550
Then just make sure

271
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:06,670
every step is done right!

272
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,550
A case doesn't just

273
00:11:07,550 --> 00:11:08,550
concern the client—

274
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,120
it concerns his entire family.

275
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:09,550
Hello.

276
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:10,440
Hello.

277
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,270
Are you looking for someone?

278
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,120
Yes, I'm looking for Mr. Wu Hao.

279
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:12,750
You should ask yourself

280
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,150
if you really did your best!

281
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,480
He's almost done there.

282
00:11:20,410 --> 00:11:21,800
It's okay. Don't be agitated.

283
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:22,790
We'll go over it later.

284
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:23,850
Alright, go ahead.

285
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,790
Mr. Wu Hao isn't big on formalities.

286
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:27,850
You can go in
as long as his office is empty.

287
00:11:27,850 --> 00:11:28,240
Thanks.

288
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:28,900
No worries.

289
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,200
Senior.

290
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,090
You're here.

291
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,790
How was it? Was this place hard to find?

292
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:39,470
No, it was okay.

293
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:40,240
Come on, sit.

294
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,320
This is how it is here.

295
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:44,690
Small place,

296
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,770
not many people,

297
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,130
but plenty of cases.

298
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,720
It's a madhouse every day.

299
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,390
A madhouse,

300
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,650
but fulfilling.

301
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,440
You're graduating this year, right?

302
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:57,790
Yes.

303
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,120
Time flies.

304
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:00,440
I still remember when you

305
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,910
first joined the Student Union.

306
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:02,600
It was written all over your face:

307
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,320
"I'm going to do something big."

308
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,360
Actually,

309
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:07,080
I still think that way.

310
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:10,840
So,

311
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,480
have you decided where you want to work?

312
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,000
The procuratorate or the court?

313
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,510
With your grades,

314
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:16,320
plenty of good employers

315
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,720
must be eager to take you.

316
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:20,320
I do have some options,

317
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:22,210
but I haven't decided yet.

318
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:24,030
Find a good employer,

319
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:25,240
get a stable job,

320
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,460
and your family will feel at ease.

321
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,390
But besides stability,

322
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,680
I want to try something else.

323
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:35,590
Have some tea.

324
00:12:36,540 --> 00:12:37,600
Your dishes are all served.

325
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,480
-Okay. Thank you.
-Enjoy.

326
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,080
Thank you.

327
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,440
I've discussed it with my mom.

328
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,000
I'll go to Longcheng tomorrow to stock up

329
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,320
and then head back to school,

330
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,260
and she'll stay in Shengcheng
to look for a shop location.

331
00:12:47,260 --> 00:12:48,170
The shop here

332
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,800
will probably be left to her.

333
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,960
Mrs. Liu has changed so much.

334
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,960
I remember
when you first arrived in Shangdu

335
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,840
to open the shop,

336
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,300
she didn't know anything.

337
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:58,840
Exactly.

338
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,630
Back then, she didn't know
how to style outfits

339
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:02,240
and barely knew any characters.

340
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,840
Over the years, she's been selling goods
by day

341
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,720
and reading Taotao's textbooks at night.

342
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,200
She knows almost all the characters now.

343
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,200
Starting a business really

344
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,060
helps you grow.

345
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:10,910
Every environment

346
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,480
has its opportunities and challenges.

347
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,670
It all comes down to what we make of it.

348
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:14,510
How things turn out ultimately

349
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,770
depends on ourselves.

350
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:18,240
So you're really not going to stay

351
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,300
for your master's?

352
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:21,600
I heard the professors at your school

353
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,130
are all hoping you'll stay.

354
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:25,120
After coming to Shengcheng

355
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:27,240
and seeing the pace of this place
with my own eyes,

356
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,150
I know that
if I don't get in the game now,

357
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,950
I'll be left behind by the times.

358
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,320
I can no longer sit calmly

359
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,270
in a classroom

360
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:33,130
and just study.

361
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:34,360
Besides,

362
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:35,870
I think this place

363
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,390
is a bigger classroom,

364
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,650
a bigger school.

365
00:13:39,070 --> 00:13:40,240
I can learn properly

366
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,330
through practice.

367
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:43,790
You're always like this.

368
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,760
You never seem lost

369
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:46,720
or afraid.

370
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:51,410
Zhou Cheng.

371
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:53,480
You went to visit Senior Wu today—

372
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:54,210
how did it go?

373
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:55,970
Pretty good.

374
00:13:56,910 --> 00:13:58,080
The law firm isn't big,

375
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,120
and there aren't many people.

376
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,390
It's only been open for 6 months.

377
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,080
It can't compare to

378
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,320
government institutions, of course,

379
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,080
but the work atmosphere

380
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:03,880
is quite good:

381
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:05,030
free,

382
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:06,200
dynamic,

383
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:07,810
and full of energy.

384
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:10,360
Just like this city.

385
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:17,410
Zhou Cheng,

386
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:21,050
my dream is to be realized in Shengcheng,

387
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,340
but your dream

388
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:24,350
doesn't necessarily have to be.

389
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,320
Of course,

390
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:27,430
I want to build a future with you.

391
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:28,480
But just like

392
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,680
what I told my mother—

393
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,900
we're not accessories to each other.

394
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,270
Don't let me influence

395
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:35,370
your decisions about your future.

396
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,080
But how can I

397
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,690
not have my future influenced by you?

398
00:14:43,690 --> 00:14:45,150
You are part of my future.

399
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:46,270
Likewise,

400
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:47,720
I hope I am

401
00:14:48,270 --> 00:14:49,600
part of your future too.

402
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:51,550
I know

403
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:53,360
how you got here

404
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,090
step by step.

405
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,120
I also know

406
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:56,600
there are things

407
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,930
you urgently want to do.

408
00:14:59,030 --> 00:14:59,960
Romantic relationship isn't

409
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,020
your top priority.

410
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:02,630
I respect that.

411
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:05,510
But sometimes,

412
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,000
it acts like a shield

413
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:09,600
between us.

414
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,120
Every time you face

415
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,200
a choice,

416
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:16,200
you use it to push me away.

417
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,320
I'm sorry.

418
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,130
Maybe I'm not so sure

419
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,560
about the future,

420
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:28,870
so I got a bit emotional.

421
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:30,980
No, Zhou Cheng.

422
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:33,050
I will think carefully

423
00:15:33,150 --> 00:15:34,280
about what you said.

424
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,100
Excuse me. Make way. Make way.

425
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:42,050
Coming through.

426
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:50,410
Not satisfied?

427
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,460
The designs have been upgraded,

428
00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:55,460
but the fabric hasn't changed much.

429
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,270
Is that the Ke Yixiong

430
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:01,600
Bai Zhenzhu mentioned?

431
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:04,030
There are inspectors in the market.

432
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:04,630
It's fine.

433
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:06,320
Besides,

434
00:16:06,610 --> 00:16:07,480
you're here with me.

435
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,340
I'm not afraid.

436
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:18,840
This shop looks pretty good.

437
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:19,870
Really?

438
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:22,280
Tell me what makes it different.

439
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,060
I can't put my finger on it,

440
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,910
but compared to other shops,

441
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,550
the styles are just better.

442
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:28,120
Our Zhou

443
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:29,250
has quite a good eye.

444
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:35,480
Feel free to look around.

445
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:37,150
These are all foreign trade goods.

446
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:37,720
Boss.

447
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,730
This is a silk blend, right?

448
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:42,700
You know your stuff, Miss.

449
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:06,190
[Clothing Tycoon Brutally Killed by
His Treacherous Young Wife]

450
00:17:07,430 --> 00:17:08,819
Chen Xiliang?

451
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,810
Yeah, that's me.

452
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:15,410
You know me?

453
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:17,030
Let me tell you, Miss,

454
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,160
you have good taste.

455
00:17:22,829 --> 00:17:23,790
Hurry up! Run!

456
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:29,120
Xiaolan,

457
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,500
why are you still here?

458
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,680
Hey, what happened?

459
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,470
What are you waiting for?

460
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:33,880
Pack up and run.

461
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:37,600
Look for yourself.

462
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:55,590
Let me tell you, Miss,

463
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:56,720
you have good taste.

464
00:17:58,790 --> 00:17:59,720
So this is

465
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:01,270
Chen Xiliang,

466
00:18:01,270 --> 00:18:02,510
the clothing tycoon who will one day

467
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:03,970
meet his end at the hands of

468
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,310
his treacherous young second wife.

469
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:06,240
This is the first time

470
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:07,590
I've met someone from my past timeline

471
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:09,050
who crossed paths with me.

472
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:11,160
Could it be that
this dream is about to end?

473
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:11,960
You can buy it as a set.

474
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,400
If you buy the set,
I can give you a discount.

475
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:14,590
If you don't like this match,

476
00:18:14,590 --> 00:18:15,310
you can swap...

477
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,350
Xiao... Xiaolan.

478
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:18,770
Not for now, thanks.

479
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,720
Nothing's wrong.

480
00:18:26,020 --> 00:18:27,070
Please come in, come in.

481
00:18:27,070 --> 00:18:27,720
Feel free to look around.

482
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:29,650
These are all foreign trade goods.

483
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:38,030
He really is the brother-in-law of

484
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:39,550
Chenyu Garment Factory's director.

485
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:41,200
He's been handling foreign trade orders

486
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,530
and recently went solo.

487
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:44,890
He should be living on this street.

488
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:46,000
They haven't heard of his family

489
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,460
having any major trouble—

490
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,720
just that his relationship with his wife's

491
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:49,770
relatives isn't very good,

492
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:51,300
and they had a few disputes.

493
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,200
Sounds like

494
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:54,550
he really is that future

495
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:55,550
clothing tycoon.

496
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:56,720
There haven't been any

497
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:58,320
life-or-death situations,

498
00:18:58,480 --> 00:19:00,590
so he probably isn't a transmigrator.

499
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:02,550
Why did you ask me
to look into Chen Xiliang?

500
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:03,410
Do you know him?

501
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:09,950
The goods of the few shops

502
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,590
we just checked out aren't great.

503
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:13,160
Only his goods stand out—

504
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:14,550
the styles and fabrics are pretty decent.

505
00:19:14,550 --> 00:19:16,000
So I wanted to see if

506
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:16,790
he's reliable

507
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:19,120
and whether I can work with him long-term.

508
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:20,500
But you ran off so fast—

509
00:19:20,790 --> 00:19:21,640
I bet he thinks

510
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,100
you didn't like his goods.

511
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:27,880
Ms. Xia.

512
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:29,790
You're in quite a good mood, huh?

513
00:19:29,790 --> 00:19:31,520
Coming all the way here for tea.

514
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:34,480
Mr. Ke, you've been following us
for quite a while.

515
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,960
So you finally decided to
come into the open

516
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:36,760
and talk to me?

517
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,880
So you're Ke Yixiong?

518
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:46,160
Is this your bodyguard, Ms. Xia?

519
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:48,880
Yes, he's my bodyguard.

520
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:51,290
And also my boyfriend.

521
00:19:54,270 --> 00:19:55,470
Pleasure to meet you.

522
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:56,840
Let's go.

523
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:03,830
It seems Ms. Bai

524
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,380
didn't pass on my message.

525
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:06,920
She did.

526
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:09,390
But I don't want to work with you.

527
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:11,770
I have no interest in illegal activities.

528
00:20:15,270 --> 00:20:16,740
In broad daylight,

529
00:20:17,030 --> 00:20:19,030
don't go spreading rumors, Ms. Xia.

530
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:19,880
We

531
00:20:20,030 --> 00:20:22,590
are all law-abiding citizens.

532
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,720
Whether you broke the law or not,

533
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,440
you know perfectly well yourself.

534
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:27,110
As for the past,

535
00:20:27,110 --> 00:20:28,550
I won't settle the score with you.

536
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:30,550
From now on, we go our separate ways.

537
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,770
I forgot to mention,

538
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,420
my boyfriend studies law.

539
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:41,090
Ms. Xia, your business has grown big,

540
00:20:41,110 --> 00:20:41,830
and your way of speaking

541
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:43,430
is certainly different now.

542
00:20:43,590 --> 00:20:44,960
I know the law, too.

543
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,400
It requires evidence.

544
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:49,240
You can't make accusations
without evidence.

545
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,030
Since

546
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:52,030
Ms. Xia looks down on us,

547
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:53,930
we're leaving.

548
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,240
Miss,

549
00:21:04,750 --> 00:21:06,080
taking the train alone?

550
00:21:07,310 --> 00:21:08,510
Where are you headed?

551
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:09,200
Home.

552
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:10,750
Home, huh?

553
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:12,960
Are you studying in school

554
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:13,920
or working?

555
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:19,920
What are you looking at?

556
00:21:21,110 --> 00:21:22,640
Those two are really weird.

557
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:25,000
They don't look like sisters at all.

558
00:21:26,770 --> 00:21:27,590
Come here, let's talk.

559
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:28,650
Come here. Come on.

560
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:32,470
Miss,

561
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:33,790
traveling alone?

562
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,330
Trying to look for a job?

563
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,210
What kind of job do you want?

564
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,440
That woman is a human trafficker.

565
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:41,100
She tried to abduct me before.

566
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:43,060
Abduct you?

567
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,240
I'll find you a place to stay
as soon as we get off.

568
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:49,170
Then I'll take you to look for a job.

569
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:50,650
Don't worry.

570
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,200
Leave it all to me.

571
00:21:53,170 --> 00:21:53,960
Where's your ID card?

572
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:54,790
Let me see.

573
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:57,570
Come on.

574
00:21:58,640 --> 00:21:59,370
Give it to me.

575
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:02,400
Miss.

576
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:03,460
Do you know her?

577
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:04,960
I...

578
00:22:06,030 --> 00:22:07,160
Who are you?

579
00:22:07,590 --> 00:22:08,690
You don't remember me?

580
00:22:08,690 --> 00:22:09,230
Alright.

581
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,700
Let me jog your memory.

582
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:11,880
Miss.

583
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,590
Traveling alone by train?

584
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:14,680
Where are you headed?

585
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:15,830
Trying to look for a job?

586
00:22:15,830 --> 00:22:17,110
I have connections.

587
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:18,570
Give me your ID card.

588
00:22:18,610 --> 00:22:19,350
I'll find you a job

589
00:22:19,350 --> 00:22:21,010
as soon as we get off the train.

590
00:22:21,370 --> 00:22:22,030
Is that what she just

591
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:22,830
told you?

592
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:25,750
Ma'am.

593
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:27,110
After all these years,

594
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:27,880
your tricks for abducting people

595
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:29,140
haven't changed a bit.

596
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:30,750
I don't know what you're talking about.

597
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:31,610
You don't know?

598
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:32,920
If I hadn't stopped you,

599
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:33,750
you would've taken

600
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:34,980
both her and her ID card away, right?

601
00:22:34,980 --> 00:22:36,160
You're slandering an innocent person.

602
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:37,200
Talking all that nonsense.

603
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,200
An innocent person?

604
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:39,630
More like a human trafficker!

605
00:22:39,630 --> 00:22:40,590
Wait, what's going on?

606
00:22:40,590 --> 00:22:41,240
Come and look, everyone.

607
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:43,070
There's a human trafficker here
abducting a young girl.

608
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,640
Don't talk nonsense, you two.

609
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,440
You're wronging an innocent person.

610
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:46,510
This is my sister.

611
00:22:47,110 --> 00:22:48,400
She's my sister.

612
00:22:48,610 --> 00:22:50,000
What are you all doing?

613
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:52,730
Is it her?

614
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:54,110
Yes, it's her.

615
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,060
Do you know her?

616
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:56,590
Don't say anything out of line.

617
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:57,590
I was helping you.

618
00:22:57,790 --> 00:22:59,190
She's my younger sister.

619
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:00,480
When we got on,

620
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:02,590
she was in a rush and didn't have time
to buy a ticket.

621
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:03,830
I was just helping her get one. Look.

622
00:23:03,830 --> 00:23:04,960
I was handling that.

623
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:07,480
She's your younger sister?

624
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:09,480
Then why did you only buy one ticket
for yourself?

625
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:10,030
Officer,

626
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,790
this person was acting suspiciously.

627
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:13,270
Even if she's not a human trafficker,

628
00:23:13,270 --> 00:23:14,030
she's a fare evader.

629
00:23:14,030 --> 00:23:15,270
You're full of nonsense.

630
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:16,880
I did buy a ticket.

631
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:18,140
Look carefully, okay?

632
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:19,380
She's the one evading the fare.

633
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:20,160
I don't know her.

634
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:21,110
You don't know her?

635
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:22,640
Wasn't she your younger sister just now?

636
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,900
Now you don't know her?

637
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:25,640
Officer,

638
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:27,410
this is this girl's ID card.

639
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,440
If I hadn't stopped them,

640
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:29,960
she'd probably be abducted by now.

641
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:30,960
I just... I...

642
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,310
Alright, stop arguing. Stop it.

643
00:23:32,310 --> 00:23:33,270
Come with me to the dining car.

644
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:34,110
We'll go to the station at the next stop.

645
00:23:34,110 --> 00:23:35,400
Why should I go?

646
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:36,070
On what grounds?

647
00:23:36,070 --> 00:23:37,240
Come with me, you all. Move it.

648
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:37,880
Come with me.

649
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:38,830
I'm not going. I'm not going.

650
00:23:38,830 --> 00:23:39,920
Passengers on both sides, please sit down.

651
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:40,790
The railway system

652
00:23:40,790 --> 00:23:41,830
will keep an eye on this person.

653
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:42,750
There isn't enough evidence this time

654
00:23:42,420 --> 00:23:44,790
[Yuezhou Railway Station Police Station]

655
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:43,610
to arrest them,

656
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:45,720
but sooner or later, we'll get evidence.

657
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:47,050
Thank you for your help.

658
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:47,920
Take this,

659
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:49,070
and you can take the next train

660
00:23:49,070 --> 00:23:49,870
to Jingcheng.

661
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:51,720
Thank you for your hard work, Officer.

662
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:52,520
Safe travels.

663
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:53,870
Thank you.

664
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,000
Thank you.

665
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:57,150
Why don't I see that girl?

666
00:23:58,960 --> 00:23:59,510
Yeah.

667
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:00,720
I saw her come out,

668
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:01,960
but I haven't seen her since.

669
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:02,440
Wait!

670
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:04,440
Here you are.

671
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:06,030
Please wait a second, you two.

672
00:24:06,030 --> 00:24:07,360
My name is Ye Xiaoqiong.

673
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,930
Thank you for helping me today.

674
00:24:11,390 --> 00:24:12,030
It's all my fault.

675
00:24:12,030 --> 00:24:13,920
I made you get separated from your friend.

676
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:14,520
It's okay.

677
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:15,880
Our friend even asked us

678
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:17,280
to make sure you're safe.

679
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:18,320
Thank you.

680
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:19,370
You're welcome.

681
00:24:20,030 --> 00:24:20,630
By the way,

682
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:22,680
you paid for my ticket.

683
00:24:23,030 --> 00:24:24,440
I wrote an IOU.

684
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:25,880
Please take it.

685
00:24:29,590 --> 00:24:31,000
Give me an address,

686
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:33,030
and I'll pay you back.

687
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:36,750
Okay.

688
00:24:38,070 --> 00:24:39,200
But the amount

689
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:40,830
needs to be changed.

690
00:24:40,830 --> 00:24:41,760
Add another 100.

691
00:24:50,110 --> 00:24:51,510
Take this 100 yuan for now.

692
00:24:51,510 --> 00:24:53,110
You can't even afford a ticket.

693
00:24:53,110 --> 00:24:54,920
What if you can't find your family?

694
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,510
How will you get back on your feet
without money?

695
00:24:56,510 --> 00:24:57,030
Take it.

696
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,160
When you have money,

697
00:24:58,160 --> 00:24:59,490
pay me back everything.

698
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:06,400
Come on.

699
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:09,210
Don't you even have that much confidence?

700
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:20,800
You are both good people.

701
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:21,960
Thank you.

702
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,130
I won't let you down.

703
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:26,300
I'll definitely pay you back.

704
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:32,880
I'm a good person?

705
00:25:33,830 --> 00:25:34,720
Wasn't I

706
00:25:34,750 --> 00:25:36,010
super fierce just now?

707
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:36,720
Yeah.

708
00:25:37,790 --> 00:25:39,320
A super fierce good person.

709
00:25:40,070 --> 00:25:40,600
Let's go.

710
00:25:41,030 --> 00:25:41,560
Let's go.

711
00:25:51,550 --> 00:25:52,940
Comrades, please sit here.

712
00:25:52,940 --> 00:25:53,310
Okay.

713
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:54,200
Okay, thanks.

714
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:54,800
Let's sit.

715
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:04,960
Kang Wei

716
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:07,640
should have arrived in
Jingcheng by now, right?

717
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,500
He should have.

718
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:11,220
We won't arrive until noon tomorrow.

719
00:26:12,510 --> 00:26:13,040
Xiaolan.

720
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,460
There's something

721
00:26:15,830 --> 00:26:16,750
I want to make clear

722
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:18,280
before we reach Jingcheng.

723
00:26:21,310 --> 00:26:22,440
I've made up my mind.

724
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,220
After graduation,

725
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:25,900
I'll go to Shengcheng.

726
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:27,750
You...

727
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,680
Just hear me out.

728
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,440
Emotionally,

729
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,200
of course, it's because

730
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,330
I want to be with you.

731
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:33,790
But this decision I'm making

732
00:26:33,790 --> 00:26:34,520
is rational.

733
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:35,870
I promise—

734
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,270
I don't feel wronged

735
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,130
or conflicted,

736
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:40,770
and I'm not sacrificing anything for you.

737
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:41,640
Back then,

738
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:43,570
you told Mayor Tang

739
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:46,720
that you liked
Shengcheng's pace of development

740
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:48,050
and its opportunities.

741
00:26:48,510 --> 00:26:49,310
Actually,

742
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:50,830
I didn't really

743
00:26:50,830 --> 00:26:52,160
feel anything at first.

744
00:26:53,030 --> 00:26:53,550
But in

745
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:54,750
Senior Wu's law firm,

746
00:26:55,310 --> 00:26:56,270
I felt it.

747
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,340
I really like it

748
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:00,170
and aspire to it.

749
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:01,900
Zhou Cheng.

750
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:03,960
About what you said yesterday,

751
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,890
I also thought about it seriously.

752
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:08,550
My way of thinking and handling things

753
00:27:08,550 --> 00:27:09,830
is a bit different from

754
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,250
most people of this era.

755
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,460
Before, I didn't consider

756
00:27:13,510 --> 00:27:14,510
whether you could

757
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:15,960
accept the way I behave.

758
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:17,590
If I made you feel

759
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:18,400
insecure,

760
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:19,830
I apologize.

761
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:21,830
But I promise

762
00:27:22,310 --> 00:27:24,240
I'll try my best to adjust myself
from now on,

763
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,590
so we can stay in sync.

764
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:26,640
No, no, no.

765
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,240
Yesterday,

766
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:30,960
I was in a bad mood.

767
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:32,470
I apologize.

768
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:34,680
Okay.

769
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,960
Then let's both stop apologizing.

770
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:38,200
Actually, I think it's good

771
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,480
that we talked things out.

772
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:41,400
It's better than having differences

773
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,000
and keeping them bottled up.

774
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:45,260
But Zhou Cheng,

775
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:47,110
I never intended

776
00:27:47,110 --> 00:27:48,110
to push you away.

777
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:50,030
I shared

778
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:52,070
my life plans with you

779
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:53,550
because I hope

780
00:27:54,110 --> 00:27:55,030
my plans

781
00:27:55,590 --> 00:27:57,250
can be compatible with yours.

782
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:04,800
I understand.

783
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,280
Thank you,

784
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:07,450
Xiaolan.

785
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:09,440
Thank you

786
00:28:10,410 --> 00:28:12,810
for being willing to
be compatible with me.

787
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:19,440
Sometimes I do wonder—

788
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:20,880
why Zhou Cheng?

789
00:28:21,550 --> 00:28:22,150
Of course,

790
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:24,920
good looks are certainly one reason.

791
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,050
But more importantly,

792
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,160
he's willing to communicate,

793
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,270
knows how to be understanding,

794
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:31,640
and can control his emotions.

795
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,370
This kind of sound personality

796
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,860
and enlightened mindset,

797
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,220
even decades from now,

798
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:38,340
will still be rare qualities.

799
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:42,270
But

800
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,800
will your parents agree?

801
00:28:50,510 --> 00:28:51,310
I don't agree.

802
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,920
Everyone else is trying to
get to Jingcheng,

803
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:55,000
but you two insist on heading outward.

804
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:55,750
Why?

805
00:28:56,070 --> 00:28:57,400
Is the path we parents planned for you

806
00:28:57,400 --> 00:28:58,330
not good enough?

807
00:28:58,480 --> 00:28:59,880
Zhou Cheng goes to
the Political and Legal Affairs Commission,

808
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:01,110
and Xiaolan goes to the Design Institute.

809
00:29:01,110 --> 00:29:03,040
It matches your majors perfectly.

810
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,400
Your mother is right.

811
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:06,070
It's not like Jingcheng doesn't have

812
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:07,750
suitable workplaces for you two.

813
00:29:07,750 --> 00:29:09,680
Why must you go to Shengcheng?

814
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,810
When I first started studying law,

815
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:15,590
I thought a

816
00:29:15,590 --> 00:29:16,750
perfect legal world

817
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:19,020
should be built from the top down.

818
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:20,400
Later,

819
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:23,590
after learning about more real life cases,

820
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:25,190
I began to think more and more

821
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:28,180
about how to put legal ideals
into practice.

822
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:31,070
When I went to Shengcheng this time,

823
00:29:31,070 --> 00:29:31,680
I actually went with

824
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,080
these questions in mind.

825
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,420
Although I dare not say

826
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:37,250
I have found the answer,

827
00:29:38,110 --> 00:29:40,030
Senior Wu's Zhiyuan Law Firm

828
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:42,190
is a worthwhile attempt.

829
00:29:44,970 --> 00:29:46,240
Senior, what made you decide

830
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:48,770
to leave the court
and start your own law firm?

831
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:53,720
Maybe it was out of

832
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:54,680
some self-important

833
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:56,810
sense of responsibility to the times.

834
00:29:57,750 --> 00:29:59,640
This may sound a bit grandiose,

835
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,840
but it's truly how I feel.

836
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:05,400
Look.

837
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:14,790
We're lucky to be born in

838
00:30:14,790 --> 00:30:15,680
such an era.

839
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,400
And having undergone so many years of

840
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,460
higher education,

841
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,350
we should shoulder

842
00:30:20,350 --> 00:30:21,950
heavier responsibilities.

843
00:30:22,830 --> 00:30:24,070
Our country establishing
the Shengcheng Special Zone

844
00:30:24,070 --> 00:30:25,530
is a brand new experiment.

845
00:30:26,750 --> 00:30:29,750
Everyone is crossing the river
by feeling for stones.

846
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,830
Shengcheng is at the forefront of
opening up.

847
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:35,240
There are more people there,

848
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:36,040
more passion,

849
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,600
and more complexity.

850
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:38,880
It needs law students like us

851
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,480
to push it forward together.

852
00:30:40,580 --> 00:30:41,980
Senior Wu said something

853
00:30:42,070 --> 00:30:43,270
that really moved me.

854
00:30:44,070 --> 00:30:44,680
He said,

855
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,030
a case

856
00:30:46,750 --> 00:30:48,510
doesn't just concern one person—

857
00:30:48,510 --> 00:30:50,170
it concerns an entire family.

858
00:30:51,550 --> 00:30:53,070
I want to stay in Shengcheng

859
00:30:53,070 --> 00:30:54,670
to work on more diverse cases

860
00:30:55,070 --> 00:30:57,400
and interact with more different people.

861
00:30:58,270 --> 00:30:58,830
This is why

862
00:30:58,830 --> 00:30:59,750
I want to

863
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:01,680
choose Shengcheng at this moment.

864
00:31:02,030 --> 00:31:02,790
To first build a

865
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:04,550
better Shengcheng Special Zone,

866
00:31:04,550 --> 00:31:05,400
and then build a

867
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,270
better China.

868
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,550
I should contribute

869
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:09,880
in whatever way I can.

870
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,720
Well said, Cheng!

871
00:31:13,790 --> 00:31:14,450
I'll go too!

872
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:15,400
Wei, sit down.

873
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,360
Don't cause trouble.

874
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,590
It seems

875
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,350
you have really thought carefully

876
00:31:23,350 --> 00:31:24,350
about this issue.

877
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:27,400
This matter

878
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,900
is not wrong in itself.

879
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,160
That you have such ambition,

880
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,090
your mother and I

881
00:31:32,550 --> 00:31:34,160
are very gratified.

882
00:31:34,900 --> 00:31:36,970
I believe your dream of practicing law

883
00:31:36,970 --> 00:31:38,910
can be realized

884
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:40,640
in both Jingcheng and Shengcheng.

885
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:41,500
But Zhou Cheng,

886
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:43,960
you have to answer me one question.

887
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:46,090
You insist on going to Shengcheng—

888
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,600
is it because of Xiaolan?

889
00:31:47,790 --> 00:31:48,240
Yes.

890
00:31:51,310 --> 00:31:51,830
But it's also for

891
00:31:51,830 --> 00:31:52,790
my own ideals.

892
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:57,930
I want to be with the person I love,

893
00:31:58,480 --> 00:31:59,740
striving for our youth

894
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,320
and our ideals together.

895
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:08,590
Go ahead then.

896
00:32:09,830 --> 00:32:10,690
Go give it a try.

897
00:32:11,050 --> 00:32:12,250
I hope you can find

898
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:13,400
the future you want.

899
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,310
Let's also wish them

900
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:20,440
a happy graduation.

901
00:32:22,130 --> 00:32:22,990
Thank you, Dad.

902
00:32:23,930 --> 00:32:25,530
We'll definitely work hard.

903
00:32:27,550 --> 00:32:29,030
You kids.

904
00:32:29,550 --> 00:32:30,640
Do you think going out to venture

905
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:31,830
is that easy?

906
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:33,350
Mrs. Guan.

907
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:34,720
The reason we have the courage

908
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:36,110
to venture out

909
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,520
is precisely because we know

910
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:40,590
that our elders have our backs.

911
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:45,030
Thank you, Mrs. Guan

912
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:46,560
and Mr. Zhou, for your care.

913
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:47,900
Come on.

914
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:51,590
Come on. Cheers.

915
00:32:59,750 --> 00:33:00,610
Just like that,

916
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,350
Zhou Cheng

917
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,270
and I

918
00:33:02,590 --> 00:33:04,590
both said goodbye to being students

919
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,680
and embarked on our own new challenges

920
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,240
in life.

921
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:09,200
Ready? Three, two, one.

922
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:14,550
Xiaolan.

923
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:19,160
Chen Qing?

924
00:33:19,220 --> 00:33:20,400
When are you taking
your graduation photos?

925
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:21,680
We took them last week.

926
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:24,200
Xiaolan, I came to tell you

927
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:26,000
that I've been selected for
government-sponsored study abroad.

928
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:27,480
I'm going to the UK next week.

929
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,350
To the UK?

930
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:29,680
That's great.

931
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:31,080
Still studying finance?

932
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:32,240
What about you?

933
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,900
Are you staying in Jingcheng?

934
00:33:34,790 --> 00:33:37,050
Zhou Cheng and I plan to go to Shengcheng.

935
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:43,000
Then...

936
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:45,810
I wish you all the best.

937
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,180
All the best to you too.

938
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:55,400
Hello.

939
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:56,400
May I ask,

940
00:33:56,750 --> 00:33:57,830
is there a lady named Liu Fen

941
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,480
staying here?

942
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:00,680
Just a moment.

943
00:34:02,310 --> 00:34:04,270
She's on the second floor, Room 202.

944
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:04,870
Thank you.

945
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:08,630
Mayor,

946
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:09,550
got it.

947
00:34:10,230 --> 00:34:10,710
Ms. Liu

948
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:11,710
is just upstairs.

949
00:34:11,710 --> 00:34:12,239
Room 202.

950
00:34:13,230 --> 00:34:14,159
Comrade Liu Fen.

951
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:16,230
Mr. Tang?

952
00:34:20,110 --> 00:34:21,040
Why are you here?

953
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:22,960
Haven't you felt like
you were missing something

954
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:24,630
these past few days?

955
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:28,360
What do you mean?

956
00:34:30,330 --> 00:34:31,080
Your watch.

957
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:33,199
You left it at the hospital.

958
00:34:38,630 --> 00:34:39,590
I forgot.

959
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,480
Thank you.

960
00:34:40,630 --> 00:34:41,480
You're welcome.

961
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,280
If anyone should be saying thanks,

962
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,030
it's me.

963
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:46,000
How are you feeling now?

964
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:47,600
I'm recovering well—

965
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:49,190
fit as a fiddle now.

966
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:50,650
That's good.

967
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:52,110
With your condition,

968
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:52,840
you need to take care of yourself.

969
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:54,370
Have more millet porridge.

970
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:54,880
Okay.

971
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:56,480
The millet porridge

972
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,480
you made last time

973
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:58,790
was arguably the best

974
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:00,330
I've ever had in my life.

975
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,010
Are you heading out?

976
00:35:04,030 --> 00:35:06,010
Xiaolan wants to come to Shengcheng.

977
00:35:06,010 --> 00:35:07,550
We can't stay in a hotel forever,

978
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:09,030
so we thought we'd go look at some houses.

979
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:09,550
True.

980
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,670
Living here

981
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,130
can be quite expensive.

982
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:16,320
My brother is here to pick me up.

983
00:35:16,720 --> 00:35:17,550
That's your brother?

984
00:35:17,550 --> 00:35:17,960
Yes.

985
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:20,860
He has a head for business.

986
00:35:21,070 --> 00:35:22,760
He even printed the company name

987
00:35:21,900 --> 00:35:23,310
[Yuanhui Decoration]

988
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:23,760
on his van.

989
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,630
It was Xiaolan's idea.

990
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:27,840
I'll get going then.

991
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:28,170
Okay.

992
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:28,760
Goodbye.

993
00:35:28,760 --> 00:35:29,280
Bye.

994
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:32,410
Comrade Liu Fen.

995
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:41,000
I want to thank you properly.

996
00:35:41,630 --> 00:35:43,360
Do you have time some other day?

997
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:44,880
I'd like to buy you dinner.

998
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,610
Is that okay?

999
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:48,880
Sure.

1000
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:51,040
Let's do it another day.

1001
00:35:51,070 --> 00:35:51,480
Okay.

1002
00:35:51,670 --> 00:35:52,200
Alright.

1003
00:35:52,550 --> 00:35:53,080
Goodbye.

1004
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:53,930
Goodbye.

1005
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:58,960
Bye.

1006
00:36:04,550 --> 00:36:05,030
Mayor.

1007
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:06,880
I'll go get the car.

1008
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:07,280
Okay.

1009
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,400
Hui'e!

1010
00:36:13,010 --> 00:36:14,520
I forgot a small bag.

1011
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:16,150
Bring it down in a bit.

1012
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:17,400
Okay.

1013
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:32,070
Here.

1014
00:36:32,250 --> 00:36:32,910
Let me, Mom.

1015
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:40,710
Mom.

1016
00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:43,510
You're going so far away.

1017
00:36:44,550 --> 00:36:45,960
Coming back during holidays

1018
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,690
would be really inconvenient.

1019
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:49,440
Once I've made some money,

1020
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:51,570
I'll take you to Shengcheng for a trip.

1021
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:55,240
Let us know when you arrive.

1022
00:36:58,590 --> 00:36:59,850
Don't worry. Alright.

1023
00:37:01,630 --> 00:37:02,110
Come on, get in the car.

1024
00:37:02,110 --> 00:37:03,170
Alright, alright.

1025
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:04,520
-Go on.
-I'm off then.

1026
00:37:06,280 --> 00:37:07,510
Treat Xiaolan well.

1027
00:37:08,700 --> 00:37:09,400
Don't worry.

1028
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:10,260
Go back inside.

1029
00:37:11,710 --> 00:37:12,320
Cheng.

1030
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:12,960
Cheng!

1031
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:14,800
I'm going to Shengcheng too.

1032
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:15,730
Why are you here?

1033
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:16,800
I've thought it through.

1034
00:37:16,800 --> 00:37:17,920
If I stay at that job,

1035
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:18,720
I'll rot away.

1036
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:21,930
Did you tell Second Uncle?

1037
00:37:21,930 --> 00:37:23,770
I did! Of course.

1038
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:24,280
Let's go. Come on.

1039
00:37:24,280 --> 00:37:25,440
Did your parents agree?

1040
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,590
They agreed. They did.

1041
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:27,480
Don't worry, Auntie.

1042
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:28,630
Let's go. Get on.

1043
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,500
Get on then.

1044
00:37:30,830 --> 00:37:31,960
We're leaving, Mom.

1045
00:37:32,070 --> 00:37:33,510
Look out for each other,

1046
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:34,070
Wei.

1047
00:37:34,110 --> 00:37:34,670
Don't worry, Auntie.

1048
00:37:34,670 --> 00:37:35,400
Don't worry, Mom.

1049
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,510
Take care.

1050
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:37,610
I'm off, Mom.

1051
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:44,000
Be careful. Easy.

1052
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,110
It's okay. It's okay.

1053
00:37:45,110 --> 00:37:46,510
Beer, drinks, peanuts, sunflower seeds.

1054
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:47,400
Anyone need anything?

1055
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:47,800
Hello.

1056
00:37:48,450 --> 00:37:50,330
We'll have 3 bottles of soda.

1057
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:52,190
And a bag of sunflower seeds, please.

1058
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:52,750
How much?

1059
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:53,360
You pay.

1060
00:37:53,550 --> 00:37:54,280
One twenty in total.

1061
00:37:54,280 --> 00:37:55,610
I'll get it. I'll get it.

1062
00:37:57,070 --> 00:37:58,280
Beer, drinks, peanuts, sunflower seeds.

1063
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,540
Anyone need anything?

1064
00:38:00,510 --> 00:38:01,510
Tell me the truth.

1065
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:03,520
Did Second Uncle really agree?

1066
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:04,320
Agree to what?

1067
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,800
I didn't even tell him.

1068
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:06,510
If I had told him,

1069
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:08,030
he definitely wouldn't have agreed.

1070
00:38:08,030 --> 00:38:09,440
Why should I listen to him?

1071
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:11,640
Young people need to go out and venture.

1072
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:14,280
But then again,

1073
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:15,150
I'm not like

1074
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:16,320
you and Xiaolan,

1075
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,840
both educated and smart.

1076
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,360
When we get to Shengcheng...

1077
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:19,800
What,

1078
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,550
the train just started,

1079
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:22,720
and you're already regretting it?

1080
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:23,680
I'm not.

1081
00:38:23,710 --> 00:38:24,670
No matter what happens, it's better than

1082
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:26,400
rotting away in that company.

1083
00:38:27,070 --> 00:38:28,000
But Xiaolan,

1084
00:38:28,480 --> 00:38:29,840
do you think

1085
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:31,030
I'm really stupid, acting like this?

1086
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:31,630
Not at all.

1087
00:38:32,050 --> 00:38:33,380
I think you're amazing.

1088
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:34,140
Very brave.

1089
00:38:34,510 --> 00:38:36,310
Much braver than I was back then.

1090
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:37,000
See?

1091
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:39,180
Xiaolan really knows
how to encourage people.

1092
00:38:39,180 --> 00:38:40,480
But when it comes to bravery,

1093
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:42,030
Xiaolan is still second to none.

1094
00:38:42,030 --> 00:38:42,960
Our Xiaolan

1095
00:38:43,150 --> 00:38:44,670
has both brains and guts.

1096
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:50,010
Come on, let's put our hands together.

1097
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:53,080
Here's to a successful venture.

1098
00:38:53,230 --> 00:38:54,800
To success!

1099
00:38:57,630 --> 00:38:58,710
By the way, Xiaolan,

1100
00:38:58,710 --> 00:38:59,880
after we arrive,

1101
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,800
do we have any

1102
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:02,290
business plans?

1103
00:39:02,670 --> 00:39:04,840
Business plans...

1104
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:07,440
Step 1:

1105
00:39:07,840 --> 00:39:09,140
find a place to live first.

1106
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:11,140
Come on, let me show you the balcony.

1107
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:13,710
It's very nice here.

1108
00:39:16,030 --> 00:39:16,440
Look.

1109
00:39:16,780 --> 00:39:17,840
Isn't it spacious?

1110
00:39:18,910 --> 00:39:19,970
You two, come here.

1111
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:21,590
That thing you mentioned just now,

1112
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:22,320
the law firm—

1113
00:39:22,810 --> 00:39:23,590
it's right over there.

1114
00:39:23,590 --> 00:39:24,760
Just keep walking straight,

1115
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,620
and it's the second one at the end.

1116
00:39:28,710 --> 00:39:29,310
Is it okay?

1117
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,320
Is this room okay?

1118
00:39:31,210 --> 00:39:32,010
Isn't it nice?

1119
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,550
Pretty good to me. What do you think?

1120
00:39:33,550 --> 00:39:34,400
I'm okay with it.

1121
00:39:34,400 --> 00:39:35,920
Alright, we'll take it then.

1122
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:36,250
Okay.

1123
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:37,590
Then let's go down and sign the contract.

1124
00:39:37,590 --> 00:39:37,880
Okay.

1125
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:38,320
Okay.

1126
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:41,230
This courtyard is nice, isn't it?

1127
00:39:41,230 --> 00:39:41,960
Pretty good.

1128
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:43,280
Spacious and clean.

1129
00:39:43,630 --> 00:39:44,110
Alright.

1130
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:45,310
We'll stay here then.

1131
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,120
Granny Yu.

1132
00:39:48,630 --> 00:39:49,880
We'll rent

1133
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:50,960
the two rooms upstairs.

1134
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:51,550
As for the courtyard,

1135
00:39:51,550 --> 00:39:53,400
I might store some goods here sometimes,

1136
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:54,530
but not for too long.

1137
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,400
How much is the rent?

1138
00:39:58,110 --> 00:39:59,840
How many people will live here?

1139
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:00,480
Two.

1140
00:40:00,710 --> 00:40:01,710
Just my mom and me.

1141
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:05,590
If you want to rent my rooms,

1142
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:07,510
you must follow my rules.

1143
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,360
First,

1144
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,510
only the two of you can live here.

1145
00:40:10,510 --> 00:40:12,880
No other men or women

1146
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,490
are allowed.

1147
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:15,190
Second,

1148
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:18,440
no loud noises in the courtyard.

1149
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:19,280
Third,

1150
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:22,190
you can use the kitchen and the courtyard,

1151
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:22,800
but

1152
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:25,400
the rent must be paid every 6 months.

1153
00:40:25,710 --> 00:40:26,590
Every 6 months?

1154
00:40:27,360 --> 00:40:28,230
Who are you?

1155
00:40:29,800 --> 00:40:30,880
This is my uncle.

1156
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,150
He might drop by sometimes

1157
00:40:32,150 --> 00:40:33,030
to visit us.

1158
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,420
He won't live here.

1159
00:40:37,030 --> 00:40:38,360
It'll be 50 yuan a month.

1160
00:40:38,550 --> 00:40:39,810
And most importantly,

1161
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:43,140
do not enter my room without permission.

1162
00:40:43,150 --> 00:40:44,000
Do not touch

1163
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:45,760
my stuff.

1164
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:46,920
Also,

1165
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,150
we are only

1166
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:49,920
landlord and tenants.

1167
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:51,190
If it's not necessary,

1168
00:40:51,190 --> 00:40:52,720
don't try to get close to me.

1169
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,480
That's all the rules for now.

1170
00:40:54,590 --> 00:40:55,440
"For now"?

1171
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,070
Do you

1172
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,030
agree?

1173
00:40:58,480 --> 00:40:58,960
We do.

1174
00:40:59,590 --> 00:41:00,190
We agree.

1175
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,280
We'll rent it.

1176
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:03,460
Please be careful.

1177
00:41:05,960 --> 00:41:06,840
What time is it?

1178
00:41:08,510 --> 00:41:09,310
Five o'clock.

1179
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,610
It's already 5 o'clock?

1180
00:41:17,510 --> 00:41:19,190
Where is this old lady going?

1181
00:41:20,070 --> 00:41:21,400
I heard from the agent

1182
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:22,400
that this old lady usually

1183
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:24,000
sweeps the streets nearby.

1184
00:41:24,030 --> 00:41:25,280
She has such a big house

1185
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,230
and charges such high rent,

1186
00:41:26,230 --> 00:41:27,560
yet she sweeps streets?

1187
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:30,280
She's got plenty of rules too.

1188
00:41:30,510 --> 00:41:32,440
She's quite an eccentric old lady.

1189
00:41:32,580 --> 00:41:34,260
To have such a big courtyard

1190
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:36,070
and speak without an accent,

1191
00:41:36,450 --> 00:41:37,710
she must be from a prestigious family,

1192
00:41:37,710 --> 00:41:39,070
educated and worldly.

1193
00:41:39,630 --> 00:41:41,890
It's normal for her to be a bit eccentric.

1194
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:43,450
She looks pretty kind to me.

1195
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:45,920
Relationships are built over time.

1196
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:46,510
I'm sure

1197
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:47,760
we can win her over.

1198
00:41:50,440 --> 00:41:52,070
The housing problem is solved.

1199
00:41:52,070 --> 00:41:52,720
Next,

1200
00:41:53,070 --> 00:41:54,720
step 2 of starting a business:

1201
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:55,920
getting communication devices.

1202
00:41:55,920 --> 00:41:56,280
Right.

1203
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:56,800
Then press down.

1204
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,230
See? It works, right?

1205
00:41:58,920 --> 00:41:59,970
Great. This is great.

1206
00:41:59,970 --> 00:42:00,710
It'll be convenient from now on.

1207
00:42:00,710 --> 00:42:01,320
Xiaolan.

1208
00:42:01,670 --> 00:42:03,000
This tiny gadget

1209
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:03,690
is so expensive.

1210
00:42:03,690 --> 00:42:04,800
Why do we have to buy it?

1211
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:09,130
♪ Along the long road ahead,
how much beauty awaits ♪

1212
00:42:05,320 --> 00:42:07,400
Communication is the bridge to everything.

1213
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:09,000
If you reply faster than others

1214
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:09,710
or receive information

1215
00:42:09,160 --> 00:42:12,750
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

1216
00:42:09,710 --> 00:42:10,710
ahead of them,

1217
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:12,600
you can seize the advantage.

1218
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:14,030
I remember the three of us

1219
00:42:13,610 --> 00:42:17,510
♪ Why pause and look back? ♪

1220
00:42:14,030 --> 00:42:15,230
had consecutive numbers.

1221
00:42:15,230 --> 00:42:17,280
Those two have couple numbers.

1222
00:42:17,510 --> 00:42:18,480
Why are you getting involved?

1223
00:42:18,070 --> 00:42:21,340
♪ My heart feels so confused ♪

1224
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:21,110
B-But consecutive numbers
are easier to remember, right?

1225
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:22,120
Sis Bai, why don't you
get a new number too?

1226
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:25,810
♪ Silently, I watch the clouds
drift in the sky ♪

1227
00:42:22,150 --> 00:42:23,320
So the four of us
can have consecutive numbers.

1228
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,800
I've had this number
for a year and a half.

1229
00:42:24,800 --> 00:42:25,440
If I change it now,

1230
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:26,760
people won't be able to reach me.

1231
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:30,920
♪ Just like you and I,
our ambitions reach far and wide ♪

1232
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:29,320
Besides clipping this on the waist,

1233
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:30,800
can we clip it somewhere else?

1234
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:31,920
Why don't you clip it on your bangs
as a hairpin?

1235
00:42:30,950 --> 00:42:34,910
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

1236
00:42:31,920 --> 00:42:32,470
Go away.

1237
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,210
Alright, alright.

1238
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:34,930
Xiaolan.

1239
00:42:35,030 --> 00:42:35,440
Cheng.

1240
00:42:35,510 --> 00:42:36,110
Let's clip them on together.

1241
00:42:35,570 --> 00:42:40,130
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

1242
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:37,960
Clip.

1243
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:40,000
With these pagers on,

1244
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:40,960
now we should walk...

1245
00:42:40,150 --> 00:42:43,380
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

1246
00:42:41,150 --> 00:42:42,230
Like this.

1247
00:42:44,140 --> 00:42:49,340
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

1248
00:42:48,710 --> 00:42:50,190
Step 3 of starting a business:

1249
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:51,110
stay grounded

1250
00:42:51,510 --> 00:42:52,920
and start with the tasks at hand.
